Frontend uses Next.js 14 with App Router.

Rules:

1. Use server components where possible.

2. Use client components only when necessary.

3. Use SSR for product pages for SEO.

4. Use SSG for static content pages.

5. Implement loading states.

6. Optimize images.

Use next/image.

7. Avoid large client bundles.

8. Use caching strategies.

9. Use API routes only when necessary.

10. Do not store sensitive data in frontend.

11. Always handle API errors.

12. Use responsive design.

13. Optimize for low bandwidth networks.
